nsion\nstarted between 8 to 10Myr ago. Two hundred members show infrared excess\ncompatible with circumstellar disks from full to debris disks. This discovery\nprovides a large sample of nearby young stellar and sub-stellar objects for\ndisk and exoplanet studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Jul 2018 16:26:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2018 16:54:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2018 17:25:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-28"}
